{"tid":136994,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【sogo佔領】中港牌七人車SOGO外逆線「埋站」 網民揶揄︰至叻係你！","createTime":"2017-02-27T13:07:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-27T13:53:18.000Z","uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"713ece865879269b2ca21c9fcbdfee84928580b3","tid":136994,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T13:07:02.000Z","msg":"人多車多的銅鑼灣軒尼詩道SOGO巴士站，傍晚離奇出現中港車逆線埋站事件。讀者巿民左先生表示，晚上6時40分途經軒尼詩道近SOGO對開，赫見一輛持中港車牌的黑色七人車逆線停車，當時有3名交通警包圍該車並向司機質問：「你喺邊度開過嚟㗎？ 」對方一度聲稱因不熟路，由東角道跨過行人路而至，但不獲警員取信，其後警員更指司機涉嫌危險駕駛，取走車匙向他作出警告：「唔熟路都唔會咁開車，你好彩無撞死人，唔係你就大鑊。」表明要拖走車輛檢驗，最終左先生離開現場未知最終結果。<br />\n<br />\n左先生批評該名司機駕駛態度有問題，「咁樣(逆線)人哋睇唔到，可能撞死人或者撞到車。」他又指現場行人路人多擠迫，該輛七人車不大可能由東角道跨路而至，估計對方或者沿糖街逆線而行肇禍。<br />\n<br />\n中港車逆線泊SOGO的相片其後在fb各討論區中熱傳，有網民紛紛估計該名司機的離奇行車路線，有網民相信他沿糖街錯誤駕出怡和街，因中間有電車路阻礙u-turn，只好一直逆線而行，直至SOGO打算轉向時終被警員截獲。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》正向警方查詢事件。"},{"pid":"f9eed03625d1d9f4b270a9a0f751ae2ee8a8c12d","tid":136994,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T13:07:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170227&amp;guid=56362702&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170227%26guid%3D56362702%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&d=vhywW4AIbf33TEOu71%2FwU8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=0f20e414\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170227%26guid%3D56362702%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&h=18ca4da3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170227&amp;guid=56362702&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"4b67ca6b562b34d83906353032d4a2b9fc5b2fd4","tid":136994,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T13:09:17.000Z","msg":"危險駕駛喎"},{"pid":"3bb39e12bde67fa0ad2fdc97e27421c373521ab8","tid":136994,"uid":5020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T13:16:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170227&amp;guid=56362702&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170227%26guid%3D56362702%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&d=vhywW4AIbf33TEOu71%2FwU8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=0f20e414\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170227%26guid%3D56362702%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&h=18ca4da3\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170227&amp;guid=56362702&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"1ce6513c9765632644ceded568af98ce8bb8dbc3","tid":136994,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T13:45:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ebc14cad731a486c14accb51dd8b07445d92eac","tid":136994,"uid":33483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T13:48:21.000Z","msg":"又放走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3faabb72a8ecb2979565230ef3581f3e40228e6","tid":136994,"uid":70415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T13:51:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又放走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一句我爸是李剛就搞掂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0534435db224cf1b31ab6a9291536c0158008aec","tid":136994,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T13:53:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>又放走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一句我爸是李剛就搞掂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n港豬幾日唔記得"}]}